{"tid":1336681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住，我係大陸人，但21/7我希望可以比我做香港人","createTime":"2019-07-21T05:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T05:58:47.000Z","uid":127735,"like":154,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a5fa018504eafe2024d07b72b014869cf1a076e2","tid":1336681,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"我大陸出世，2003年沙士後黎香港，屋企不聞世事，不吃人間煙火。<br />\n<br />\n我搶左你地12年免費教育，對唔住<br />\n我搶左你地公共醫療資源，對唔住<br />\n我搶左你地香港土地住屋，對唔住<br />\n我搶左你地今年既四千蚊，對唔住（所以派得未呀）<br />\n<br />\n我搶左你地香港，對唔住<br />\n<br />\n我無膽，我廢，我唔敢企前面，我唔敢勇武，我無錢捐，我無勇氣承擔法律責任<br />\n<br />\n我驚比警打，我驚比警拉，我驚有案底，我驚毀前途<br />\n<br />\n但係，我唔想番大陸住！<br />\n<br />\n即使我只係敢和平遊行，企後排，幫湊到一個人頭，但我依然選擇21/7會一個人出黎<br />\n<br />\n你呢？"},{"pid":"d50dd79b5dff7928d50b195fed38c57b886240e6","tid":1336681,"uid":263219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"愛你"},{"pid":"bbd7e0e4714a53a0985891ebf1abdddd8feab40a","tid":1336681,"uid":204352,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"我依家代表香港人歡迎你入籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd567b5c82d1dca3ed7f16e4254ce9eba6c6c090","tid":1336681,"uid":275238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:19:41.000Z","msg":"推爆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee28ed69683d87e634ba90cccf7904135c8153e1","tid":1336681,"uid":178684,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"見你入鄉隨俗 打繁體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算你啦"},{"pid":"bd43280ba70675f942970d17d5889523ad1cebbd","tid":1336681,"uid":63400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:21:22.000Z","msg":